The paper deals with wireless communication systems and their optimization for higher data rates and energy efficiency. The paper discusses radio frequency (RF) energy harvesting, improper Gaussian signaling, and full-duplex communication mode. These topics are closely related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and computer communication (cs.COM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
